for low-
and high-income taxpayers from 1988 to 1999:
Year  Individual   Individual     Overall 
<TEXT>
<P>
      Under $25,000Over $100,000  
1988-- 1.03         11.41          1.57    
1989-- 1.03          6.45          1.29    
1990-- 0.55          5.55          1.04    
1991-- 0.94          5.64          1.17    
1992-- 0.78          5.28          1.06    
1993-- 0.74          4.03          0.92    
1994-- 1.04          2.94          1.08    
1995-- 1.96          2.79          1.62    
1996-- 2.00          2.85          1.67    
1997-- 1.44          2.27          1.28    
1998-- 1.14          1.66          0.99    
1999-- 1.36          1.15          0.90    
