<HEADLINE> AP Top News at 9:17 p.m. EDT  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Saturday, April 15, 2000
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Police Make Mass Arrests in D.C.
</SUBHEAD>
